images.description: A tall and thin model with long straight blond hair strutting on a runway in a white minidress with red and black wide stripe accents, carrying a large blue bag.
Players in a ringette game in motion on the ice.
Four astronauts in orange space suits posing for a portrait.
A crowd holding a banner protesting fast fashion and its impact on climate.
A model with flowing blond hair in a lace garment posing for an ad.
Panoramic view of Rome’s cityscape with historical domes and buildings.
An electric eel among aquatic plants in an underwater habitat.
A brewery’s sterile interior with stainless steel tanks and pipes for beer production.
A woman with long, wavy brown hair stands with a slight smile on the red carpet.  She is wearing a sleeveless, blue dress with a center front zipper that is unzipped about 4 to 5 inches.
Couple in formal wear on a red carpet.
Whole and opened pomegranate with seeds.
A lively street scene with a diverse crowd of people on bicycles, some wearing colorful outfits.
